OL,3,CConcerns over accessibility of
OL,4,CJersey's new ferry provider
OL,6,FA passenger says the broken lift on a
OL,7,FDFDS Seaways ferry means her trip from
OL,8,FJersey to the UK will take almost
OL,9,Ftwice the amount of time.
OL,11,FSue Tidswell came to Jersey on a four-
OL,12,Fand-a-half-hour journey to spend a
OL,13,Fweek with family.
OL,15,FHowever, due to issues with mobility
OL,16,Fand the lift on the Levante now
OL,17,Fbroken, Sue has to either struggle up
OL,18,Fstairs or take a nine-hour ferry to a
OL,19,Fdifferent destination.
