OL,3,CConcerns over accessibility of
OL,4,CJersey's new ferry provider
OL,6,FDFDS has apologised for the
OL,7,Finconvenience caused, adding that
OL,8,Fparts to repair the lift are on their
OL,9,Fway.
OL,11,FBut Sue says it's "disgraceful in this
OL,12,Fday and age" that the vessel isn't
OL,13,Faccessible.
OL,15,FShe explains: "At least until 30th
OL,16,FMay, disabled people can't travel. And
OL,17,Fthat's so wrong, and I think that
OL,18,Fmakes me more angry and more wound up,
OL,19,Fbecause I know how hard it is.
