OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F387A1745438447
OL,3,CConcerns over accessibility of
OL,4,CJersey's new ferry provider
OL,6,F"It's so difficult at the best of
OL,7,Ftimes, and they've got a new service
OL,8,Fthat's not adequate or accessible for
OL,9,Fsomebody with a mobility issue."
OL,11,FSue adds that she was already anxious
OL,12,Fabout the trip back, and says she has
OL,13,Fspent the rest of her holiday worrying.
OL,15,FShe admits: "All the time I'm on
OL,16,Fholiday, I'm thinking, 'What's the
OL,17,Freturn going to be like? How am I
OL,18,Fgoing to manage to get home?'
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
