PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F387A1745438447
OL,3,CConcerns over accessibility of
OL,4,CJersey's new ferry provider
OL,6,F"I'm pretty strong and pretty rough
OL,7,Ffor me in this state, but I'm still
OL,8,Freally worried about how it's going to
OL,9,Fbe."
OL,11,FDespite the issues with the lift, Sue
OL,12,Fsays she "couldn't fault" the staff
OL,13,Fwho looked after her on her first
OL,14,Fjourney.
OL,16,FSteve runs the Maison Des Landes, a
OL,17,Fspecialist hotel for people with
OL,18,Fdisabilities.
