OL,3,CConcerns over accessibility of
OL,4,CJersey's new ferry provider
OL,6,FHe says the lift must become
OL,7,Foperational, as many who travel to the
OL,8,Fhotel do so by sea.
OL,10,FSteve explains: "It's easy to get on
OL,11,Fthe boat, but without the lift, you
OL,12,Fwouldn't be able to. You need a
OL,13,Fmechanical lift to operate.
OL,15,F"Having the facilities where you are
OL,16,Flooked after and you've got lifts and
OL,17,Framps and staff looking after you
OL,18,Fmakes a huge difference.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
