OL,3,CConcerns over accessibility of
OL,4,CJersey's new ferry provider
OL,6,F"I think it would affect people's
OL,7,Fdecisions of what they're going to
OL,8,Fbook and whether they do book or not."
OL,10,FA DFDS spokesperson stated: "The
OL,11,Fpassenger lift on board the Levante
OL,12,Fvessel is currently out of action and
OL,13,Fawaiting parts for its repair, which
OL,14,Fare expected to arrive in a few weeks.
OL,16,F"Passengers travelling on this route
OL,17,Fare being contacted and offered
OL,18,Falternative travel arrangements to and
OL,19,Ffrom the UK.
